Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.46,0:01:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要好好的看清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.76,0:01:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為終有一天你也會繼承這份使命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.15,0:02:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個就是『調律』
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.11,0:02:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『調律』
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.01,0:02:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光? 『調律』是指什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.61,0:02:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將妖怪送往那個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.19,0:02:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個世界?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.62,0:02:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是 殺掉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.46,0:02:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 爺爺 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.59,0:02:44.69,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,1000)}{\pos(320,340)}你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.33,0:02:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也並不是什麼稀奇的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.97,0:02:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾帶來見下面也是很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.70,0:02:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 但是 也不僅僅是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.19,0:02:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個啊 因為大家都評價說很可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.10,0:03:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也想親眼所見一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.73,0:03:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…妳遇到的就只有那自稱亂射魔的小兄嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.06,0:03:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.92,0:03:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是謹慎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.37,0:03:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不露尾巴  那隻狐狸混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.63,0:03:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狐狸？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.91,0:03:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有只喜愛惡作劇的狐狸在城鎮周圍徘徊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.74,0:03:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 妳不用太過於在意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.37,0:03:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來 可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.30,0:03:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.23,0:03:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東鈴 居住在櫻真鎮這段期間 要暫時約束妳的行動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.19,0:03:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全信任曾讓城鎮陷於危險之中的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.89,0:03:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是我 還是這座城鎮都不會如此寬容的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.14,0:03:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.42,0:03:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是去上學的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.44,0:03:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是找尋能寄住的打工地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.58,0:03:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那邊工作 自己掙取學費
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.23,0:03:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.25,0:03:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這些
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.77,0:03:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這些？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.29,0:03:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有什麼問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.52,0:03:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我引起了那麼大的騷亂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.30,0:04:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不是知道後才來這裡的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.52,0:04:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是為妖怪而建的城鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.21,0:04:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.25,0:04:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我還有公事在身
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.24,0:04:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詳細的事情就問秋名吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.81,0:04:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.55,0:04:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了 我把秋名先生帶來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.75,0:04:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好喲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.30,0:04:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有段時間沒見了吧 秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.34,0:04:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶然也來這裡露個臉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.26,0:04:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有很多的事情要忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.01,0:04:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是妖怪生活商討所所長 比泉秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.60,0:04:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鎮上生活的全面安排都是由他那管理的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.10,0:04:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有什麼問題的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.76,0:04:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.62,0:04:40.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.46,0:04:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.68,0:04:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼人類會做這種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.75,0:04:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡可是妖怪的城鎮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.26,0:04:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被討厭了呢 秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.44,0:04:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.77,0:05:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼都沒做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.62,0:05:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是妖怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.35,0:05:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼和人類的關係會如此親近呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.98,0:05:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城鎮有它的規則所在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.71,0:05:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保護妖怪的規則
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.20,0:05:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在這個城鎮住下的話 就得聽秋名的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.74,0:05:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被『七鄉』所包圍的範圍之內大致都張開了結界
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.11,0:05:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然看了地圖就會瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.65,0:05:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本上只需要記住\N過橋後就是安全的 那就沒什麼問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.57,0:05:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊是車站
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.34,0:05:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大部分的商店都聚集在那
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.02,0:05:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都知道有很多的妖怪在 妳也不用太在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.28,0:05:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫院在那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.75,0:05:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是專門為妖怪而設立的 所以不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.55,0:05:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.62,0:05:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 這個也是我的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.05,0:05:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 車站前有銀行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.82,0:05:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.73,0:05:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說了嗎 在車站前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.82,0:05:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是說事務所
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.65,0:05:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說了嗎 由我來帶路
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.18,0:05:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪邊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.27,0:06:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.69,0:06:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.59,0:07:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想早點賞花啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.65,0:07:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻色遍染的城鎮 一定相當美麗的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.49,0:07:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,區長 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.84,0:07:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.29,0:07:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是『七鄉』嗎 去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.76,0:07:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有那個必要 已經不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.76,0:07:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去元老院吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.35,0:07:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.32,0:07:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳覺得把城鎮的吉祥物用狸怎麼樣 狸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.95,0:07:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會不會給人種被哄騙了的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.99,0:07:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比豬要好點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.59,0:07:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣說起來\N妳聽說炸豬排店有會笑的豬的圖畫沒？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.80,0:07:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有啊 有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.28,0:07:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來是打算去吃蒙古烤肉的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.17,0:07:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但結界外面有隻狐狸 去吃不成啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.16,0:07:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個我也不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.82,0:08:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼 城鎮的吉祥物用哺乳類可不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.02,0:08:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊貓之類的不也很可愛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.80,0:08:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個可是猛獸哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.70,0:08:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.02,0:08:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在著冷氣的房間裡像糟老頭似的懶來懶去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.19,0:08:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來完全就像個懶蟲的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.58,0:08:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實很凶暴的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.83,0:08:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.60,0:08:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.58,0:08:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給它取名叫 牛舌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.55,0:08:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是食材嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.70,0:08:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去是挺悠哉 但貌似能看到某現實的未來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.27,0:08:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.48,0:08:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳這概念才是沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.45,0:08:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來的很晚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.21,0:08:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.83,0:08:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好喲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.83,0:08:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.26,0:08:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了 桃華一直在等你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.44,0:08:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在說什麼呀 言葉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.38,0:08:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 抱歉 被元老院給傳召了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.41,0:08:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個叫鈴的孩子來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.38,0:08:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是上次的那個『不死人』嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.35,0:08:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒來過這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.68,0:09:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是有個公園的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.87,0:09:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.64,0:09:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.31,0:09:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在找事務所
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.59,0:09:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道那個人類在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.28,0:09:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙 對公務的怠慢也太隨意了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.90,0:09:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位…不是人類嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.55,0:09:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？ 妳是說恭助？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.30,0:09:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.42,0:09:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把角亮出來給妳看看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.12,0:09:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.52,0:09:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  去事務所吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.24,0:09:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打電話給秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.48,0:09:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.89,0:09:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在妖怪的城鎮 讓人類當所長真是夠奇怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.12,0:09:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實如此 我從前也是這樣想的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.41,0:09:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.34,0:09:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭助
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.24,0:09:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.61,0:09:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那人的危機意識也太過薄弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.14,0:09:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所談論的問題的要點不是這吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.34,0:09:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 現在眼前就有一個正在困惑中的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.37,0:10:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話雖如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.30,0:10:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該也很清楚 他是城鎮必不可少的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.51,0:10:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必不可少？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.74,0:10:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.37,0:10:11.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠『調律』的只有比泉家的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.83,0:10:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『調律』？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.51,0:10:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將妖怪的靈魂送入另一個的世界\N也就是妖怪的世界能力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.14,0:10:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個就是『調律』
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.68,0:10:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.98,0:10:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是為了解救在這個世界暴走的妖怪\N也只有這個方法了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.94,0:10:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用秋名的手…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.68,0:10:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是被稱為解救嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.29,0:10:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.24,0:10:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.08,0:10:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在了 在了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.95,0:10:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.18,0:10:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.60,0:10:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.10,0:10:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桃華 沒有必要幫這種男人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.98,0:10:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別稱呼我為「這種男人」啊  妹控
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.59,0:10:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.92,0:10:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹控
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.72,0:10:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.08,0:10:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹控
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.65,0:10:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別躲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.20,0:10:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹控
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.76,0:10:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼好笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.18,0:11:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是殺了妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.79,0:11:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.57,0:11:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為是妖怪 所以殺了它也沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.86,0:11:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為對方不是人類 就可以這樣開懷大笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.28,0:11:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.25,0:11:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名不是這樣的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.66,0:11:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.39,0:11:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.21,0:11:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.59,0:11:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  是我解釋的不好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.95,0:11:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.62,0:11:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前爺爺也是這麼說我的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.92,0:11:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實也可以看成是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.26,0:11:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是不順利啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.38,0:11:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.29,0:11:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭助 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.72,0:11:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 是把她送回事務所吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.65,0:11:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.18,0:12:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 沒有印章的話 簽個名就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.65,0:12:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遷入申請只是個形式罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.75,0:12:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.51,0:12:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…這公寓附近有人類居住嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.10,0:12:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.38,0:12:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.86,0:12:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有兩戶人家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.04,0:12:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.90,0:12:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有其他地方可選了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.87,0:12:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我們也沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.78,0:12:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是人類 也不都是壞人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.03,0:12:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別是這鎮上住著的人都已經習慣和妖怪為鄰了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.98,0:12:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 老在意這些的話 連學校都去不了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.85,0:12:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.32,0:12:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這點傷應該完全沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.39,0:12:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你們妖怪不都很強的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.09,0:12:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.49,0:12:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准說人類的語言 說幾句妖怪語來聽聽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.68,0:13:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…不要…不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.45,0:13:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類無論怎麼傷害妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.78,0:13:11.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著妖怪難受也都若無其事一般
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.15,0:13:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想不會有這樣的事的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.97,0:13:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 我看起來也是那樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.56,0:13:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我原本也是人類 看起來像那類人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.98,0:13:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳一定有著「人類的時候真好」這樣的想法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.96,0:13:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『花』
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.47,0:13:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為現在也不壞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.47,0:13:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺掉嗎…很難回答啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.95,0:14:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆炸？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.09,0:14:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 根據居民所述 是突然爆炸的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.37,0:14:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.33,0:14:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想是由於妖怪的力量暴走所致
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.40,0:14:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的事可能嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.39,0:14:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有前例
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.15,0:14:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來 再來做點愉快的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.61,0:14:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能 從未聽說過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.46,0:14:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是照片
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.97,0:14:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當事人原本就是一個擁有很強妖力的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.33,0:14:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其力量在瞬間爆發出來…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.64,0:14:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那樣的 怎麼可能暴走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.65,0:14:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當事人口述說 在力量爆發之前 身體發熱 無法控制
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.09,0:14:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口述說？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.48,0:14:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被某種東西附身上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.00,0:14:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是這麼認為的 但卻找不到任何痕跡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.27,0:15:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會議中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.56,0:15:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐  又發生了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.86,0:15:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我自己也不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.32,0:15:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在自己未能察覺的情況下 妖力就暴走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.62,0:15:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請詳細告訴我經過
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.29,0:15:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才已經跟警察說明過了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.00,0:15:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩妳再說明一次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.17,0:15:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭助 秋名在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.84,0:15:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給他打過電話 沒人接
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.87,0:15:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像也沒在事務所裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.13,0:15:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 我絕對不要干消滅妖怪的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.43,0:15:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你所有背負的使命 終有一天你會明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.49,0:15:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承受著那樣的罪過\N正是因為你有著要保護的事物存在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.58,0:15:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為比泉家之人 這是非做不可之事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.89,0:15:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使命嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.11,0:15:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在動搖什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.02,0:16:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.16,0:16:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.44,0:16:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學校我也不會去的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.85,0:16:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不是和姬約定好了的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.56,0:16:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為我不知道會同人類一起生活
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.99,0:16:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和人類一起生活的話 很快就會習慣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.36,0:16:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們認為沒事 而我卻很困擾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.61,0:16:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.84,0:16:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是已經決定好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.30,0:16:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了保護城鎮  就必須進行『調律』
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.28,0:16:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.28,0:16:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.99,0:16:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是被說了幾句 就變得如此心神不定
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.07,0:16:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的決心就只有這點程度嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.89,0:16:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有決心 但…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.71,0:16:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.48,0:16:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被人稱為殺人者 我也沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.31,0:16:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了保護城鎮 你的使命…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.61,0:16:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.07,0:16:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名你所做的並沒有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.75,0:16:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從小在這城鎮中長大 身為妖怪的我是如此堅信的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.13,0:16:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣都還不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.28,0:16:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的…我知道的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.62,0:16:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.66,0:17:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.70,0:17:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在事務所 在事務所發生了暴走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.59,0:17:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.28,0:17:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是鈴 東鈴的妖力正在暴走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.53,0:17:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼 布下結界 不要讓人接近
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.74,0:17:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言葉 恭助 先防止暴走造成更大的破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.58,0:17:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.09,0:17:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『籠』
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.71,0:17:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『籠』
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.77,0:17:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『籠』
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.68,0:17:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這要怎麼樣才能阻止啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.09,0:18:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.54,0:18:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來 我抑制的這段時間 你們快去避難
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.57,0:18:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭助
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.73,0:18:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.01,0:18:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用『調律』的話 便能減輕妖力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.40,0:18:43.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鈴呢 要把她送走嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.25,0:18:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.82,0:18:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.46,0:18:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『調律』
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.10,0:19:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老實的呆在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.61,0:19:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.26,0:19:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.58,0:19:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.47,0:19:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別靠近我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.45,0:19:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.01,0:19:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是打算殺掉我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.18,0:19:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要殺掉我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.70,0:19:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.79,0:19:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.24,0:19:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實 比泉家的人殺害過妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.66,0:19:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若無其事 毫無痛苦 一直都在…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.82,0:19:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.26,0:19:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好怕 求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.22,0:19:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在內心卻一直都明白「不能做這樣的事」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.60,0:20:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是這樣 如果這力量能保護他人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.95,0:20:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有堅信這力量是必須的妖怪的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.72,0:20:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.96,0:20:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『調律』
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.20,0:20:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影子？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.56,0:20:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來不是鈴的力量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.03,0:20:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這傢伙在操縱著妖怪的力量而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.20,0:20:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『調律』…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.81,0:21:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺努力的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.29,0:21:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越來越期待了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.97,0:21:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭妖怪的人類是不會做這樣的事的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.75,0:21:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…帖符的替代品
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.38,0:21:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 妳要喜歡那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.75,0:21:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說啦 別用哺乳類的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.29,0:21:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.25,0:21:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可愛嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.95,0:21:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.65,0:21:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算用這當食物的名字你也這麼認為？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.98,0:21:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛舌
